      <h2>Multi-source ingestion with persona-driven adversarial input</h2>
      <p>Fusion ingests Custody, Fund Accounting, and Middle Office data and harmonises identifiers, units, and field names. Our Reader does the same — but is also stress-tested against persona-driven adversarial inputs (column drift, unit mismatch, legacy format collisions). The current Reader persona is shown below, with the specific perturbations applied.</p>

      <div class="pill-row">
        <span class="pill cyan" id="reader-persona">Senior FA Ops</span>
        <span class="pill" id="reader-perturb">No perturbations</span>
        <span class="pill" id="reader-result">Clean parse</span>
      </div>

      <div class="tabs">
